### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  Consultas
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Listar consultas (USER)  → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/consultas
Authorization: Basic {{userAuth}}

### Cadastrar consulta (ADMIN)  → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/consultas
Authorization: Basic {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataConsulta": "2026-06-25T10:00:00",
  "observacoes": "Consulta de retorno",
  "pacienteId": 1,
  "medicoId": 1
}

### Cadastrar consulta com paciente inexistente (ADMIN)  → 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/consultas
Authorization: Basic {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataConsulta": "2026-06-25T10:00:00",
  "pacienteId": 9999,
  "medicoId": 1
}
